cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.DC

This paper is about automatic machine learning (AutoML) for deep learning, specifically focusing on optimizing both hyperparameters and network architectures using evolutionary algorithms. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper also includes experiments on medical image classification and natural language analysis, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing).
